  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7280327/" class="title-link">一片冰心在玉壶</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7280327"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/115965274/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/115965274/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">天地一浮萍</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-12-24"
      class="main-meta">2014-12-24 23:56:16</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7280327_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这本书一直在读，而且还想反复的去读，我觉得还应该和他的女婿周锡瑞出版的《叶：百年动荡中的一个中国家庭》联系起来读，我喜欢看一个家族的发展史，透过一个家族的发展，能感受那个年代的大环境，叶家经历了好多年，几代人的努力，从安徽一步步走到了天津，并在天津扎根，开...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7280327_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7280327_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










